{"tid":589903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衞警告「X疾病」或隨時爆發 可殺全球數百萬人","createTime":"2018-03-12T07:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T03:40:58.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9165206d2d6a4e71a7dab93a9ad128cb591a217f","tid":589903,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>世衞警告「X疾病」或隨時爆發 可殺全球數百萬人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Uocg1l_WAMc6r5qy9pVOCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzU0O2g9NjA0O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-03-11/b9d17d70-2522-11e8-a11d-d5c1193bf372_X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUocg1l_WAMc6r5qy9pVOCw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzU0O2g9NjA0O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-03-11%2Fb9d17d70-2522-11e8-a11d-d5c1193bf372_X.jpg&h=ad19b613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">世衞警告「X疾病」或隨時爆發 可殺全球數百萬人_</span><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】世界衞生組織近日公布2018年可能導致嚴重國際爆發的疾病，除了伊波拉病毒和寨卡病毒等較為人熟悉的疾病外，還包括一種被稱為「X疾病」（Disease X）的致命病原體。專家警告，「X疾病」爆發的條件已經成熟，可從多種源頭形成，或隨時大爆發，而且人畜傳染機率高，可殺全球數以百萬計病人。<br />\n<br />\n八大高危疾病包括伊波拉病毒、拉薩熱、克里米亞剛果出血熱、尼帕病毒、中東呼吸綜合症冠狀病毒、沙士、寨卡病毒以及「X疾病」。<br />\n<br />\n世衛於發表的聲明中指，「X疾病」代表已知道一種嚴重國際流行病，可能會由目前未知的病原體引起。專家承認不知「X疾病」具體是甚麼，但警告疾病可從多種源頭形成，並可能於任何時候爆發。<br />\n<br />\n世衛認為，下一次大規模傳染病更有可能來自大自然。世衛科學顧問羅汀根（John-Arne Rottingen）警告，「X疾病」可能會經由人畜共通傳染病爆發，例如愛滋病病毒就相信是從猴子身上傳染給人類；而寨卡病毒亦是由蚊子傳播的。<br />\n<br />\n世衛擔心，流感病毒繼續快速變異，新的外來病原體不斷從動物身上傳播到人類身上。<br />\n<br />\n世衞希望將「X疾病」正式命名為「未知的下一次大流行」，將有助於促使全世界的研究人員準備應對突然爆發的疫情。<br />\n<br />\n另外，流感威脅亦不容忽視，世衛警告下一次全球流感大爆發可能在明天便會發生，或僅僅在200天內便可以殺死3300萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-x%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85-%E6%88%96%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E5%8F%AF%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-073900377.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-x%25E7%2596%25BE%25E7%2597%2585-%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA-073900377.html&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ66zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f1af8525\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-x%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85-%E6%88%96%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E5%8F%AF%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-073900377.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ba0d2b0d632359c023e189e0deac960a150ed82","tid":589903,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e814fd1d2a36e242012d6b069781c611d3375093","tid":589903,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"病毒戰？"},{"pid":"c39396b0c9c2d8a0aecdbcd8771c676607eb3898","tid":589903,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"T Virus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06f84c60bdbf1927f8ffd4c7ec340a34f4ff703","tid":589903,"uid":172915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8918c501ff85fabdfda5e5a75368f84ae63f68","tid":589903,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"好空泛喎<br />\n姐係好似個市隨時會冧<br />\n但係唔知幾時同點解冧"},{"pid":"be8ded22e51d79295270c4fefee9a2ed605a0f2d","tid":589903,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"真係鞭鞭聲"}]}